eTV says it has been deeply saddened by the death of veteran actor Sandy Mokwena. Mokwena, well-known for playing Bra Eddie Khumalo on the soapie Scandal, passed away on Thursday at the age of 68, due to natural causes. Mokwena has played in numerous South African shows including Soul City, Generations, Khumbulekhaya, Yizo Yizo, Zero Tolerance and Dead End. -TNA Reporter